# Files that tessl install creates (re-created live on stage during the Stage 3 install beat).
# Keep these gitignored so a fresh clone has zero pre-loaded plugin context, and the
# `tessl install` beat shows real creation, not just an update.
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md

# Gradle + Kotlin build outputs
**/build/
**/.gradle/
**/.kotlin/
**/out/

# JetBrains IDE
.idea/
*.iml

# macOS
.DS_Store

# Logs / scratch
*.log
